        public StatUV​(double value,
              U unit,
              double min,
              double max,
              double minimum,
              double maximum)
        Parameters:
        value - The initial value of this stat.
        unit - The unit of this stat. This is only important to specify dimension and to specify what units the constructor will use now.
        min - The initial min value. This is intended to be able to be changed.
        max - The initial max value. This is intended to be able to be changed.
        minimum - The absolute minimal value. This is a hard limit that should not be possible to change.
        maximum - The absolute maximal value. This is a hard limit that should not be possible to change.

       throws UnitMismatchException
        Adds to the value of this stat.
        Parameters:
        value - numerical value of unit vector
        unit - unit U of unit vector
